  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162970/extras/c267f3290254b95b0d896ea415255815.apng?t=1696530965\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162970/extras/c267f3290254b95b0d896ea415255815.poster.avif?t=1696530965\" class=\"bb_img\" width=40 height=40 /></picture></span> PLATFORMING ACTION <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162970/extras/d2b2fdaa844eb7d4841304ec618c12ad.apng?t=1696530965\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162970/extras/d2b2fdaa844eb7d4841304ec618c12ad.poster.avif?t=1696530965\" class=\"bb_img\" width=40 height=40 /></picture></span> </h2><br><br>In Bargain Platformer you must choose a run size and try to finish it with the highest score possible.<br><br>To achieve that you must collect coins and get to the finish line as fast as possible. <br><br>Be careful though some jumps are hard and traps are everywhere.<br><br>Oh... and enemies lurk in the worst places.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162970/extras/c267f3290254b95b0d896ea415255815.apng?t=1696530965\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162970/extras/c267f3290254b95b0d896ea415255815.poster.avif?t=1696530965\" class=\"bb_img\" width=40 height=40 /></picture></span> FEATURES <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162970/extras/d2b2fdaa844eb7d4841304ec618c12ad.apng?t=1696530965\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162970/extras/d2b2fdaa844eb7d4841304ec618c12ad.poster.avif?t=1696530965\" class=\"bb_img\" width=40 height=40 /></picture></span> </h2><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Cool pixel art assets and animations<br></li><li> Randomly selected free roam levels from a map pool<br></li><li> Thematic cups of 10 or more levels<br></li><li> Bonus levels and challenges<br></li><li> Special level conditions that affect gameplay<br></li><li> Several different traps and enemies <br></li><li> Sections with precise platforming<br></li><li> Frequent updates</li></ul>",
