icture></span> </h2><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Cool pixel art assets and animations<br></li><li> Randomly selected free roam levels from a map pool<br></li><li> Thematic cups of 10 or more levels<br></li><li> Bonus levels and challenges<br></li><li> Special level conditions that affect gameplay<br></li><li> Several different traps and enemies <br></li><li> Sections with precise platforming<br></li><li> Frequent updates</li></ul>",
